{"tid":1480614,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"講第N次: 818有衝突都唔會係示威者問題，到時勿怪示威者","createTime":"2019-08-17T11:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T11:51:16.000Z","uid":161430,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"59cdbad0540168add2f818bf0d1b61c529472b1a","tid":1480614,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:25:00.000Z","msg":"1. 聽日人多到迫出維園外，百份百會發生，迫到咁上下，入<span style=\"color: red;\">夜時，黑警就會開始無預警下舉旗，跟住十秒時間後就衝出去拉人打人。</span><br />\n<br />\n因此，示威者唔做任何野，佢都會搞你，詳情諗返早幾日深水埗，仲有今日旺角都係咁。<br />\n<br />\n因此即使好多人話<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日要完全和理非</span>，但<span style=\"color: red;\">有衝突場面仍然必然發生，<br />\n有衝突場面 = / = 示威者 亂黎</span>。<br />\n聽日其實冇示威者會亂黎，和理非同勇武都唔會點亂黎。<br />\n<br />\n2. 一早有消息話會有大陸人着黑衫扮示威者，同時又有警察扮示威者<br />\n<br />\n既然<span style=\"color: red;\">人鬼難分</span>，更加唔應該一發生事就第一時間怪示威者，<span style=\"color: red;\">請小心fact check</span>一切先。<br />\n<br />\n記住聽日有衝突，一定係黑警責任，到時唔好成個連登又互屌左先。"},{"pid":"758bbee3907fdbecb384e65748d1ae80bb94faa7","tid":1480614,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"7dcb549489452fd60f26aaf1a8e6fea4fb290073","tid":1480614,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"4e6cd189f62fdefafe5fe6c5d1233616738ec5e6","tid":1480614,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 維園見</span></span>"},{"pid":"7167e0a0fd8c05a1c01380919dead4a5f1b9b3fb","tid":1480614,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"818 維園見"},{"pid":"7233c22ea9b37a573178154b30e3c6894de765e8","tid":1480614,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6760d07f20d3e0947ba9da4bec34140a90375d","tid":148